title: I Was Reincarnated as a Baby God - Novel Updates
author: Yeon Bae Krim   연백림
description:
The Princess of the Roahim Empire was murdered by her very own brother.

She was killed and then framed for the murder of their father. What!?

Reincarnated into a new life!

A second life that she never thought of.

But isn’t there something a little weird?

The ruler of the northern part of the Roahim Empire.

Grand Duke Elharan said that even the Emperor, the owner of the Idelbador Mountains and the Ice Wall, had to treat them with respect…..>
